title: Tin Foil Hat Ep 15: Who Shot Tupac and Biggie?
description:
Welcome to another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. Sam and Ryan welcome black freemason, Chris Blackburn, to the show to help interview the Director of 2pac- Assassination: Battle For Compton, RJ Bond. One this episode we discuss...
1) Being a Freemason
2) Corruption in Compton
3) Deathrow Records
4) Who Shot Tupac
5) Corruption of The Rampart Police Department
6) Who Shot Biggie
